OL,3,CTributes paid to Crossroads actor Tony
OL,4,CAdams after his death at 84
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to Crossroads
OL,7,Factor Tony Adams, who has died at the
OL,8,Fage of 84.
OL,10,FHe died in the Sussex County Hospital
OL,11,Fin Brighton on Saturday (25 October)
OL,12,Fwith his wife Christine by his side.
OL,14,FHe was born in Anglesey, Wales, in
OL,15,F1940 and later trained as an actor at
OL,16,Fthe Italia Conti theatre school.
