OL,3,CTributes paid to Crossroads actor Tony
OL,4,CAdams after his death at 84
OL,6,FFollowing performances on the stage,
OL,7,Fhe made his name as Dr Neville
OL,8,FBywaters in the 1970s soap General
OL,9,FHospital and appeared in the Dr Who
OL,10,Fseries The Green Death.
OL,12,FIn 1978, he took on the role of
OL,13,Faccountant Adam Chance in ITV soap
OL,14,FCrossroads ` the role for which he
OL,15,Fbecame best known for.
OL,17,FThe series ended in 1988 after more
OL,18,Fthan 4500 episodes, with Tony Adams
OL,19,Fstaying until the end.
