OL,3,CTributes paid to Crossroads actor Tony
OL,4,CAdams after his death at 84
OL,6,FHe was one of the original cast
OL,7,Fmembers, including Jane Rossington and
OL,8,FKathy Staff, who returned when the
OL,9,Fsoap was revived in 2001.
OL,11,FTony then appeared in the stage
OL,12,Fversion of Chitty Chitty Bang Bang at
OL,13,Fthe London Palladium Theatre, where he
OL,14,Fplayed Grandpa Potts, in 2004.
OL,16,FIn 2023, he had a cameo role in Nolly
OL,17,F` a three-part drama created by
OL,18,FRussell T Davies which tells the story
OL,19,Fof Crossroads actress Noele Gordon.
