OL,3,CTributes paid to Crossroads actor Tony
OL,4,CAdams after his death at 84
OL,6,FActor Augustus Prew, who played Tony
OL,7,FAdams in the drama, described him as a
OL,8,F"magical man" during interviews at the
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FMichael Rose, of The Michael Rose
OL,12,FOrganisation Ltd, paid tribute to
OL,13,FAdams as an "absolute joy" and a
OL,14,Ftalented actor, dancer and singer.
OL,16,F"He was one of the warmest gentlemen
OL,17,Fyou could wish to work with," Mr Rose
OL,18,Fsaid.
