OL,3,CTributes paid to Crossroads actor Tony
OL,4,CAdams after his death at 84
OL,6,F"He was an absolute joy. He was a
OL,7,Fdancer originally but there was
OL,8,Fnothing Tony couldn't do.
OL,10,F"He was a very accomplished actor, he
OL,11,Fwas a really good dancer and singer.
OL,13,F"He played Grandpa Potts in Chitty
OL,14,FChitty Bang Bang and was a joy to have
OL,15,Fin the company, as he was in every
OL,16,Fcompany.
OL,18,F"We shall miss him."
